sentence: (+) Etsy ( ETSY ), which was gaining nearly 9% as its diluted EPS rose to $0.32 in Q4 from $0.36 a year earlier, outpacing analysts' estimates of $0.28 in a Capital IQ poll.
Revenue rose to $200.03 million from $136.27 million a year ago, also exceeding the $194.77 million estimate.

(+) AutoZone ( AZO ) was trading more than 9% higher after i t report ed fiscal Q2 earnings of $11.49 per share, up from $10.38 in the comparable period a year ago and exceeding the estimate of $10.00 from analysts polled by Capital IQ.
(-) Home Depot ( HD ) was down nearly 3% as the company booked fiscal Q4 profit of $2.09 per share, up from $1.52 per share in the prior-year period.
Excluding certain special items, net income would have been $2.25 per share, which came in higher than the $2.16 per share Street estimate provided by Capital IQ, if comparable.
